title: Stumped on a cursive font
content:
This font is sooo familiar but I have gone through tons of stuff online and can’t find it. Can anyone ID the cursive font?

[http://yque.com/vegtaslikchi.html](http://web.archive.org/web/20091215143505/http:/yque.com/vegtaslikchi.html "http://yque.com/vegtaslikchi.html")
author: ny4gracie

comments.content:
What, the «Vegans»?  
Looks like Brush Script, [squooshed](http://web.archive.org/web/20091215143505/http:/typophile.com/wiki/squooshed) and skewed and stuff.

In case you meant the scratchy navigation script, that’s [Chiller](http://web.archive.org/web/20091215143505/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/letraset/chiller/).

- Mike Yanega
